{"tid":2187860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性分析]Tesla已經見頂","createTime":"2020-09-04T01:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T16:52:56.000Z","uid":2429,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ed83298614d854edfee74b8f6565001aafdb3e","tid":2187860,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:47:29.000Z","msg":"圖表上咩三黑烏鴉、rsi超買就唔講啦，今次齋講基本層面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先美國大選已經踏入直路，華爾街一向支持民主黨，一定會沽爆美股做低侵侵，未來兩個月Tesla可謂低處未算低。之於拜登贏咗之後，一定會親支，咁Tesla就會畀支那強制技術轉移，到時恒馳股價會超越Tesla。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果侵侵連任，共和黨一向親傳統油商，一定打壓新能源產業。同中國關係又差，習近平隨時國有化佢間上海工廠回血，到時好似匯豐咁供股吊命。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結：無論兩黨邊一面贏，Tesla都係死路一條，好快變仙股，大家可以用黎貼牆紙留畀個孫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c01d47a0b4ca6bf1c25ea9491116208e41716871","tid":2187860,"uid":134522,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:48:29.000Z","msg":"升緊又唔講跌完先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b3f430da8eec0dbfdfd7d2740eb324f293774e","tid":2187860,"uid":20368,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3832168824c942293e8daa91d64b2e2014814405","tid":2187860,"uid":60393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T01:52:30.000Z","msg":"樓主好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5583ef9c17b757513f2cca798939fb4a5588c8","tid":2187860,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:04:55.000Z","msg":"成班蟹軍不願面對。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a32beb4c311c4fe376042b118a01fd0f90a9c1","tid":2187860,"uid":5178,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"一句講晒啦 400齊頭易記<br />\n無可能穿"},{"pid":"24a980